snippet.title: Feed Us Lost Island Flash Game Playthrough
snippet.description:
Feed Us Lost Island is one of the biggest expansions of the series.  The map is much larger, and there's a lot of missions!  On top of that there's a huge amount of new special items and abilities.  You can fly, breath outside of water, and launch missiles at your enemies.

Unfortunately since the game is glitched I got stuck at 26.  I did a lot of the objectives and visited everything so I am probably not going to go thru the entire game again.  The rest of the missions seem a bit repetitive anyway, mostly sinking tons of more boats, and eating people. 

▬▬ How to Play  ▬▬
There are still many good ways to play flash games.  Such as Flashpoint, the Y8 Browser, and Ruffle.
Y8 - https://www.y8.com/download-app
Flashpoint Infinity - https://flashpointarchive.org/downloads
